Transform data before putting them in the view.
1/ lowercase pipe.  changes a string to its
lower class representation.
<h2>{{name | lowercase }}</h2>
2/ uppercase:
{{name| uppercase}}
3/ titlecase:
{{name|titlecase}}
cap first letter of each word
4/ slice:
{{name|slice: beg# end#}}
if you just have a beg it will slice from therer on. 
